name: SetUtils_hashCodeForSetTest
description: Unit tests for the SetUtils.hashCodeForSet method, which calculates the hash code for a given set.

test_cases.name: testHashCodeForSet_NullSet
test_cases.description: Tests the hash code calculation for a null set, expecting a result of 0.

test_cases.name: testHashCodeForSet_EmptySet
test_cases.description: Tests the hash code calculation for an empty set, expecting a result of 0.

test_cases.name: testHashCodeForSet_NonEmptySet
test_cases.description: Tests the hash code calculation for a non-empty set, expecting the sum of the hash codes of its elements.

test_cases.name: testHashCodeForSet_SetWithNullElements
test_cases.description: Tests the hash code calculation for a set containing null elements, expecting the sum of the hash codes of the non-null elements.
